data.description: Very nice move in ready 3 bedroom ranch close to high school. Easy care hard surface flooring. Kitchen will comes equipped with all appliances, including washer & dryer, & were new in 2022. Generously sized living room. Seller will be installing a new roof prior to closing. The 1.5 car detached garage offers storage. You'll have a 1.5 car detached garage in the back yard (no driveway to this building) perfect for a workshop, storage or party room.
